full_title: I Like It by Cardi B, Bad Bunny & J Balvin
title: I Like It

primary_artist.name: Cardi B, Bad Bunny & J Balvin

description.plain:
Featuring Latin grooves, an energetic horn section, and an infectious trap beat, “I Like It” sees Cardi explaining what she likes whilst also flaunting her Latin heritage, much like she did on Ozuna’s “La Modelo.”

The Latin influences of the song are underpinned by a sample from Pete Rodriguez’s 1967 boogaloo song “I Like It Like That”, and guest features from Puerto Rican rapper Bad Bunny, and Colombian reggaetón star J Balvin.
